NK005(ca)011:0: dpal chen yang dag lha dgu'i dbang gi cho ga bde chen 'jug ngogs zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK005(ca)011:1: dpal chen yang dag lha dgu'i dbang gi cho ga bde chen 'jug ngogs zhes bya ba /
NK005(ca)011:2: bla ma dang dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)011:3: dpal ldan bde chen 'gyur med he ru ka /
NK005(ca)011:4: stong nyid khro mo dbyings kyi dbang phyug mar //
NK005(ca)011:5: dgyes rol rdo rje khra 'thung yang dag dang //
NK005(ca)011:6: dbyer med drin can bla mar phyag bagyi'o //
NK005(ca)011:7: bde chen mchog gi grong khyer nyams dga' bar //
NK005(ca)011:8: myur bder bgrod pa'i thabs tshul bla na med //
NK005(ca)011:9: dbang bskur cho ga rnam dag gzhung don gyi //
NK005(ca)011:10: snying po bde chen 'jug ngogs 'dir gsal bya //
NK005(ca)011:12: he ru ka gal po las /
NK005(ca)011:13: rang bzhin lhun grub dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)011:14: slob ma rab gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK005(ca)011:15: bya bral rdzogs pa'i man ngag bstan //
NK005(ca)011:17: slob ma 'bring gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK005(ca)011:18: bskyed rdzogs grub pa'i man ngag bstan //
NK005(ca)011:19: gzugs brnyan bsnyen sgrub dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)011:20: tha ma'i slob gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK005(ca)011:21: rim gyis blo sbyangs man ngag bstan //
NK005(ca)011:22: zhes gsungs pa bzhin slob ma mchog dang 'bring dang
NK005(ca)011:23: tha ma'i rigs can rnams la ye shes dang ting
NK005(ca)011:24: nge 'dzin dang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du skal
NK005(ca)011:25: pa dang mtshams pa'i dbang bskur nas de dang de'i
NK005(ca)011:26: man ngag rnams ston par gsungs pa las /
NK005(ca)011:27: phyi ma'i dbang du byas nas bsgrub pa'i rim pa la /
NK005(ca)011:28: dang po sa gzhi yongs su bzung //
NK005(ca)011:29: gnyis pa sta gon gnas pa dang /
NK005(ca)011:30: nub gsum pa la 'jug par bya //
NK005(ca)011:31: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du shes par bya ba las /
NK005(ca)011:33: lhag gnas kyang cho ga gzhan dang /
NK005(ca)011:35: bsgrub cing mchod pa la sogs pa'i las kyi rim
NK005(ca)011:36: pa'i khog dbub rnams ni dkyil chog las shes pa'i
NK005(ca)011:38: 'dir slob mar dbang bskur ba'i cho ga la /
NK005(ca)011:39: sbyor ba sta gon gyi cho ga dang /
NK005(ca)011:40: dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba'i cho ga'o //
NK005(ca)011:42: lha dang bum pa sta gon gyi cho ga rdzogs pa'i rjes nyid du bya ba'am /
NK005(ca)011:43: dngos gzhi dkyil 'khor bshams bkod zin nas nang bar
NK005(ca)011:44: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa byed rgyu'i nyin snga ma'i
NK005(ca)011:45: dgong kha'i dus su byas kyang rung ste sgrub rdzas
NK005(ca)011:46: dkyil 'khor rnams yol bas bsgribs te mi mthong bar
NK005(ca)011:47: byas / slob dpon gyi nye logs su so shing /
NK005(ca)011:54: mar me dri dang bcas pa'i mchod pa rnams bshams nas /
NK005(ca)011:55: cho ga dngos la bcu gcig las dang po gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:56: slob ma rnams khrus byas gral la 'khod nas /
NK005(ca)011:57: chos bshad thon mong ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)011:59: 'di ni sgrub pa lag len du ston pa rol pa'i rgyud sde lnga las /
NK005(ca)011:60: thugs kyi tan+t+ra he ru ka rol pa'i rgyud kyi
NK005(ca)011:61: bye brag dpal khrag 'thung gi gal po che'i rgyud
NK005(ca)011:62: kyi rjes su 'brang ba yang dag zla gam dgu
NK005(ca)011:63: pa'i dkyil 'khor du smin byed kyi dbang nyid bskur
NK005(ca)011:64: ba skabs su babs pa yin zhing /
NK005(ca)011:65: dbang de la'ang sbyor dngos rjes gsum las skabs 'dir
NK005(ca)011:66: sbyor ba sta gon gyi bye brag slob ma lhag
NK005(ca)011:67: par gnas pa'i chos rnams sgrub par byed pa yin
NK005(ca)011:68: pas / de'i slad du thog mar khyed rang rnams
NK005(ca)011:69: kyi lus longs spyod dus gsum dang 'brel ba'i dge
NK005(ca)011:70: tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas pa thams cad gcig tu
NK005(ca)011:71: bsdoms nas 'bul ba'i mos 'dun bgyis te zhing khams
NK005(ca)011:72: pas / 'bul mdzod / ces brjod de man+dala 'bul /
NK005(ca)011:73: slar yang me tog dang bcas pa'i thal mo sbyar bas btud de /
NK005(ca)011:74: slob dpon sangs rgyas dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)011:75: thar pa chen po'i grong khyer du //
NK005(ca)011:77: mgon po'i thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:79: gnyis pa spro ba bskyed pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:81: rigs kyi bu dag tshur gshegs shig /
NK005(ca)011:82: khyed ni theg pa chen po'i rigs //
NK005(ca)011:83: gsang sngags zab mo'i snod yin pas //
NK005(ca)011:84: gsang sngags spyod tshul cho ga 'di //
NK005(ca)011:85: khyod la yang dag bshad par bya //
NK005(ca)011:86: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'das pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:87: de bzhin gang dag ma byon dang //
NK005(ca)011:88: da ltar bzhugs pa'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK005(ca)011:89: de dag kun gyis gsang sngags kyi //
NK005(ca)011:90: cho ga zab mo 'di mkhyen pas //
NK005(ca)011:91: dang po byang chub shing drung du //
NK005(ca)011:92: thams cad mkhyen pa'i chos sku brnyes //
NK005(ca)011:93: gsang sngags lta spyod zab mo 'dis //
NK005(ca)011:94: skyob pa rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK005(ca)011:95: bdud sde shin tu mi bzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)011:96: dpung chen dag kyang 'di yis bcom //
NK005(ca)011:97: de nas kun mkhyen thob bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)011:98: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK005(ca)011:100: gsum pa rgyud sbyangs pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:101: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK005(ca)011:102: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)011:103: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK005(ca)011:104: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK005(ca)011:105: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK005(ca)011:106: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)011:107: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK005(ca)011:108: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK005(ca)011:109: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK005(ca)011:110: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK005(ca)011:111: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK005(ca)011:112: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK005(ca)011:113: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK005(ca)011:114: dag pa gsum gyi lus dbul lo //
NK005(ca)011:115: tshe rabs bgrangs ba'i las rnams kun //
NK005(ca)011:116: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK005(ca)011:117: zhes yan lag brgyad pa tshar gsum gyis rgyun bshags dang //
NK005(ca)011:118: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK005(ca)011:119: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK005(ca)011:120: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK005(ca)011:121: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)011:122: zhes sho lo ka gcig gis khyad par gyi sems gnyis bskyed /
NK005(ca)011:123: bzhi pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:126: slob dpon gyi snying gar zla ba la gnas pa'i h+aum yig sngon po /
NK005(ca)011:127: de las 'od zer ram yig tu spros pas slob
NK005(ca)011:128: ma'i nyer len gyi phung po sdig sgrib bag chags
NK005(ca)011:129: dang bcas pa bsregs shing sbyangs nas /
NK005(ca)011:130: +aahh+aum du gyur pa bdag gi zhal du zhugs sku'i
NK005(ca)011:131: dbyibs brgyad rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi pad+mara babs
NK005(ca)011:132: pa he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis par gyur
NK005(ca)011:134: de'i gnas gsum du rdo rje dang bcas pas bdud rtsi'i thig le byas la /
NK005(ca)011:139: mgrin par pad+ma la +aah snying gar rdo rje la
NK005(ca)011:140: h+aum gis mtshan pas sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rang
NK005(ca)011:141: bzhin du byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:143: de ltar byin gyis brlabs pa de mchod pa'i yul du byas nas /
NK005(ca)011:145: mdun du spos dang mar me /
NK005(ca)011:146: snying gar dri'i byugs pa rnams kyis mchod cing gsal bar bskyed par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:147: drug pa dngos grub kyi ltas brtag pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:148: bla ma'i mdun du ba byung lngas khru gang gru bzhir ba ko tsam du byugs /
NK005(ca)011:149: dri bzang gi chag chag gdab /
NK005(ca)011:150: me tog gi tshom bu lnga bkod pa gdod nas
NK005(ca)011:151: grub pa'i rigs lnga'i rang bzhin du mos pa la
NK005(ca)011:152: / u dum+w+aa ra dang a shwat+sha la sogs pa'i
NK005(ca)011:153: so shing srid du sor bcu gnyis pa skyon dang
NK005(ca)011:154: bral ba bdud rtsi'i chus bkrus shing rtse mor me
NK005(ca)011:155: tog bcings pa 'khyil ba'i sngags kyis btab nas slob
NK005(ca)011:156: ma shar du phyogs pa'i thal mo'i bar du /
NK005(ca)011:157: badz+ra dzi ha sam b+ha ra pra ti ni h+aum /
NK005(ca)011:161: zhes so rtsa drud nas tshom bu'i steng du dor ro //
NK005(ca)011:164: tshom bu dbus ma la gtad na mchog dang /
NK005(ca)011:167: phyogs bzhir zhi sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)011:168: mtshams su phra mo'i dngos grub rnams 'grub cing /
NK005(ca)011:169: phyir lhung na dngos grub mi thob pas bskyar ro //
NK005(ca)011:170: bdun pa khyor chu blud pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:171: rmi lam gsal bar bya phyir /
NK005(ca)011:172: pam las byung ba'i dri bzang gi chu +aahh+aum bzlas pa /
NK005(ca)011:173: hrih bi shud+d+ha d+har+m+aa sarba p+aa pam ni ts+aa s+ya
NK005(ca)011:174: bi shwa d+ha ya sarba bi kalpa a pa na
NK005(ca)011:175: ya h+aum / zhes brjod nas khyor bar byin pa lan gsum du 'thung zhing kha lag kyang bakru'o //
NK005(ca)011:176: brgyad pa srung skud gdags pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:177: rmi lam gyi bar chad bsrung ba'i phyir /
NK005(ca)011:178: gzhon nu mas bkal ba'i skud pa dmar po brkyang
NK005(ca)011:179: ba lus tshad dang mnyam pa sum bltab tu bsgril
NK005(ca)011:180: ba rdo rje'i mdud pa gsum dang ldan pa la
NK005(ca)011:181: ye shes kyi srad bu bstims nas pho'i dpung ba
NK005(ca)011:182: g.yon dang mo'i g.yas pa la bcings te /
NK005(ca)011:183: bud+d+ha mee tre rak+sha rak+sha sarba na h+aum a ham /
NK005(ca)011:184: zhes brjod cing chu dang bcas pa'i rdo rjes rgya gram du reg la /
NK005(ca)011:186: zhes rgyas btab nas bsrung bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:187: dgu pa ku sha gtad pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:188: rmi lam rno bar bya phyir /
NK005(ca)011:189: h+aum bzlas pa'i ku sha'i chun po gnyis /
NK005(ca)011:191: zhes sngas dang stan gyi don du byin no //
NK005(ca)011:192: bcu pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:193: spro ba brtan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK005(ca)011:194: bskal pa bye ba du ma ru //
NK005(ca)011:195: sngon du sdig pa byas pa gang //
NK005(ca)011:197: de dag zad par 'gyur yin na //
NK005(ca)011:198: grags pa mtha' yas sngags spyod pa'i //
NK005(ca)011:199: tshul la gnas na smos ci dgos //
NK005(ca)011:201: mdor na gsang sngags kyi tshul 'di ni dkon la
NK005(ca)011:202: phan yon che ba yin pas blo ma 'gyur bar
NK005(ca)011:203: nyams su len par gyis shig /
NK005(ca)011:205: spros pa la dga' na dbang gi gegs brgyad bshad na'ang skabs su bab par 'gyur ro //
NK005(ca)011:206: bcu gcig pa rmi lam brtag na ni /
NK005(ca)011:207: khyed rnams do nub sngar gtad pa'i ku sha'i sngas
NK005(ca)011:208: stan la seng+ge'i nyal stabs kyis dus gsum gyi rnam
NK005(ca)011:210: thun gsum gyi tha ma la rmi lam mthong ba
NK005(ca)011:211: gang yin pa nang par nga la smra bar gyis
NK005(ca)011:212: shig / ces gdams nas las thams cad pa'i sngags kyis bsrungs la gtad do //
NK005(ca)011:213: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi yol ba bsal te /
NK005(ca)011:214: sta gon gyi lha la mchod cing bstod nas snyan gsan phab /
NK005(ca)011:216: zhes pas nam mkhar btegs nas slar yang mchod par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:217: sngon du sgrub dkyil bshams zin na ni 'degs mi dgos so //
NK005(ca)011:221: bdag bskyed kyi rjes chog rnams rdzogs par byas nas nyal ba'i rnal 'byor gyis nyal te /
NK005(ca)011:222: nangs par slob ma rnams rmi lam bzang na spro ba bskyed cing dge ba spel /
NK005(ca)011:223: ngan na las sngags dang drag po'i sbyin sreg sbyang ba rnams bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:224: de dag ni nub gnyis pa'i bya ba'o //
NK005(ca)011:225: gnyis pa dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba la /
NK005(ca)011:228: bdag nyid 'jug cing slob ma la dbang bskur ba dang bzhi las /
NK005(ca)011:229: dang po gnyis dkyil chog tu blta zhing /
NK005(ca)011:230: gsum pa bdag nyid 'jug pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:231: slob dpon dkyil 'khor gyi nub nas shar du phyogs te //
NK005(ca)011:232: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)011:233: zhes sogs kyis rig pa'i me tog dor nas bdag
NK005(ca)011:234: nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs te nus ldan du bya
NK005(ca)011:236: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK005(ca)011:237: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)011:240: zhes pas slob ma gzhug par gsol ba btab nas gnang ba nod par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:241: bzhi pa slob mar dbang bskur ba la gnyis las /
NK005(ca)011:242: dang po dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la bcu gnyis las /
NK005(ca)011:243: dang po sngon 'gro'i yan lag ni /
NK005(ca)011:244: slob ma byang chub la yid ches pa'i rtogs pas rgyud dag cing /
NK005(ca)011:245: 'phangs pa med pa'i yon gyis sloob dpon mnyes par byed pa rnams /
NK005(ca)011:246: las bum gyi chus khrus byas /
NK005(ca)011:247: phyag dang yon gyi dang po phul nas dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)011:248: gyi yol ba'i phyi rol shar phyogs su 'khod pa
NK005(ca)011:250: 'o ma nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams
NK005(ca)011:251: cad kyi don du bla na med pa yang dag
NK005(ca)011:252: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi slob pa'i zung 'jug
NK005(ca)011:253: gi ngo bo nyid kha sbyor yan lag bdun ldan
NK005(ca)011:254: gyi go 'phang rin po che gang zhig tshe 'di
NK005(ca)011:255: nyid la mngon du bsgrub par bya /
NK005(ca)011:256: de'i ched du gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam
NK005(ca)011:257: gyi 'jug sgo dang po smin byed dbang gi rim
NK005(ca)011:258: pa rnams legs par nod nas lam zab mo bskyed
NK005(ca)011:259: rdzogs kyi rim pa gnyis la tshul bzhin du bslab
NK005(ca)011:260: par bagyi'o snyam pas byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK005(ca)011:262: chos nyan pa'i kun tu spyod pa rnams kyang blang
NK005(ca)011:263: dor ma 'dzol bar bgyis te legs par gsan 'tshal
NK005(ca)011:264: / de la gang zhig gsan par bya ba'i chos
NK005(ca)011:265: kyi rnam grangs kyang spyir bdag cag gi ston pa
NK005(ca)011:266: thabs la mkhas shing thugs rje chen po dang ldan
NK005(ca)011:267: pa de nyid kyis gdul bya'i sems can rnams kyi
NK005(ca)011:269: bsam pa'i rjes su 'gro ba'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK005(ca)011:270: dpag tu med pa zhig bskor bar mdzad pa yin
NK005(ca)011:271: yang / re zhig spang gnyen gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK005(ca)011:272: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa'i bye brag brgyad
NK005(ca)011:273: khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por chos kyi phung po'ang
NK005(ca)011:274: de snyed cig tu grangs nges pa yin te /
NK005(ca)011:276: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)011:277: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)011:278: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)011:279: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)011:280: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)011:281: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)011:282: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)011:283: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)011:284: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)011:285: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa kun //
NK005(ca)011:286: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs par zad //
NK005(ca)011:288: de yang gzhung dang man ngag tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK005(ca)011:289: gzhung mtshan nyid phar phyin gyi theg pa dang /
NK005(ca)011:290: man ngag gsang chen rdo rje'i theg pa gnyis su 'du ba yin te /
NK005(ca)011:292: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK005(ca)011:293: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:298: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK005(ca)011:299: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:300: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas nas //
NK005(ca)011:301: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK005(ca)011:302: zhes bshad pa ltar khyad chos bzhi'i sgo nas khyad
NK005(ca)011:303: par du 'phags pa gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa
NK005(ca)011:304: nyid yin zhing / de las yang shes byed rgyud
NK005(ca)011:305: sde'i rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod
NK005(ca)011:306: kyang lta spyod tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK005(ca)011:307: spyod pa gtso bor ston pa bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK005(ca)011:308: lta ba gtso bor ston pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud
NK005(ca)011:309: de gnyis su gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag
NK005(ca)011:311: de yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud tsam dang /
NK005(ca)011:312: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud gnyis su yod pa la /
NK005(ca)011:313: 'di ni rnal 'byor bla na med pa la nang
NK005(ca)011:314: gses bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum ston pa'i gzhung rgyud
NK005(ca)011:315: lung man ngag gsum yod pa'i dang po rgyud ma
NK005(ca)011:316: h+aa yo ga / de la'ang bskyed rim thabs kyi
NK005(ca)011:317: cha dang rdzogs rim rlung gtso bor byed pas gsal
NK005(ca)011:318: stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su
NK005(ca)011:319: len pa ma h+aa'i ma h+aa ste pha rgyud gsang
NK005(ca)011:320: ba 'dus pa la sogs pa dang /
NK005(ca)011:321: bskyed rim gyi spros pa shas chung zhing shes rab
NK005(ca)011:322: rdzogs pa'i rim pa khams byang chub kyi sems thig
NK005(ca)011:323: le gtso bor byed pas bde stong rnam par mi
NK005(ca)011:324: rtog pa'i tshul du nyams su len pa ma h+aa'i
NK005(ca)011:325: a nu ste ma rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang
NK005(ca)011:326: dpal yang dag la sogs pa dang /
NK005(ca)011:327: bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa
NK005(ca)011:328: thig rlung gsum las bskyed pa'i bde gsal rnam par
NK005(ca)011:329: mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK005(ca)011:330: khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la gtso
NK005(ca)011:331: bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len pa ma
NK005(ca)011:332: h+aa'i a ti ste gnyis med kyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul
NK005(ca)011:333: d+r+wa ba la sogs pa las /
NK005(ca)011:335: sgrub pa lag len du ston pa rol pa'i rgyud sde lnga las /
NK005(ca)011:336: thugs kyi tan+t+ra he ru ka rol pa'i rgyud kyi
NK005(ca)011:337: bye brag dpal khrag 'thung gi gal po che'i rgyud
NK005(ca)011:338: kyi rjes su 'brangs ba yang dag zla gam dgu
NK005(ca)011:339: pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba skabs su babs
NK005(ca)011:340: pa yin / de la dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK005(ca)011:341: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la brten nas go 'phang gi chos rgyud la 'jog pa'i las kyis /
NK005(ca)011:342: rgyud kyi dri ma byang ba'am nyams smad par byas shing /
NK005(ca)011:343: thar ba'i myu gu mngon du skyes pa'am /
NK005(ca)011:344: skye nges kyi sa bon khyad par can gsos thebs
NK005(ca)011:345: pas lam sgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi
NK005(ca)011:346: nus pa mthu can du smin par byas pa ste
NK005(ca)011:347: / sa bon gsos thebs pa'i cha de sngags kyi sdom pa'ang yin la /
NK005(ca)011:349: nges tshig ni a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK005(ca)011:350: mngon par gtor bas na dbang ste /
NK005(ca)011:351: sbyang bya sgo gsum gyi dri ma gtor zhing 'khrud par byed pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)011:352: yang mngon par blugs pas na dbang ste /
NK005(ca)011:353: lam sgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi nus pa khyad par can rgyud la 'jog pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)011:354: de ltar yang brtag gnyis las /
NK005(ca)011:355: gtor dang blugs pa zhes bya ba //
NK005(ca)011:356: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK005(ca)011:358: dbye na phyi yi dbang dang /
NK005(ca)011:362: de yang dbang bskur ba ni dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin la /
NK005(ca)011:363: de la'ang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK005(ca)011:364: sems can shin tu gdul dka' gang //
NK005(ca)011:365: sdom pa 'dzin par mi byed cing //
NK005(ca)011:366: dad dang ldan pa med pa yang //
NK005(ca)011:367: 'jug pa nyid ni dgag mi bya //
NK005(ca)011:368: zhes pas re zhig dbang gi snod du ma gyur pa'i gang zag yin na'ang /
NK005(ca)011:369: dkyil 'khor du bcug pa tsam la 'gal ba med par gsungs mod /
NK005(ca)011:370: dkyil 'khor du ma bcug pa la dbang bskur ba ni nam du'ang mi rung ste /
NK005(ca)011:372: dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba rnams kyi mdun du ma smra zhig ces gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)011:374: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK005(ca)011:375: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK005(ca)011:376: zhes gsungs pa ltar sta gon du gnas pa yan chad song nas /
NK005(ca)011:378: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bya ba dang /
NK005(ca)011:379: rdo rje slob ma'i bya ba gnyis yod pa las /
NK005(ca)011:380: slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa /
NK005(ca)011:382: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas 'jug pa rnams chad lhag med par sngon du grub /
NK005(ca)011:383: da khyed rang slob ma rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK005(ca)011:384: lha dang skal pa mnyam pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos dang /
NK005(ca)011:385: zhugs nas dbang nod pa'i bya ba gnyis las /
NK005(ca)011:386: 'dir 'jug pa'i yan lag khrus dang bgegs bsal ba sngon du song nas /
NK005(ca)011:387: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi
NK005(ca)011:388: dad pa la dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos rnams
NK005(ca)011:392: de nas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags kyis btab pa'i stod g.yogs dang smad dkris bgo ba'am /
NK005(ca)011:394: rigs kyi kha dog can gyi dar ram ras sgo
NK005(ca)011:395: srung gi sngags sam a kham wi ra h+aum gis
NK005(ca)011:397: rin po che'i me tog gi phreng ba /
NK005(ca)011:400: gnyis pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:401: sngags kyi dngos grub la rtse gcig tu mos pas thal mo sbyar ba btud de /
NK005(ca)011:402: byang chub rdo rjes sangs rgyas la //
NK005(ca)011:403: ji ltar mchod chen bgyis pa ltar //
NK005(ca)011:404: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)011:405: nam mkha'i rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)011:406: zhes lan gsum gyi gsol ba gdab /
NK005(ca)011:407: gsum pa spro ba dri ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:409: khyod ni dga' ba ci la dad //
NK005(ca)011:412: bdag ni skal bzang bde chen la //
NK005(ca)011:413: rab dgyes 'phrul la bdag dga' ste //
NK005(ca)011:414: mchog tu dga' la bdag daga'o //
NK005(ca)011:416: bzhi pa nang du drang ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:417: slob ma la slob dpon gyi lag gi rdo rje la 'dzin du bcug ste /
NK005(ca)011:418: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde ba'i //
NK005(ca)011:419: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK005(ca)011:420: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zung //
NK005(ca)011:421: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK005(ca)011:422: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK005(ca)011:423: ser sna spang ba'i dang yid kyis //
NK005(ca)011:424: gtor zhing rang sems brtan por bzung //
NK005(ca)011:425: yang dag grub pa'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK005(ca)011:426: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi nang du drangs par mos te yol ba bsal /
NK005(ca)011:427: lnga pa phyag bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:428: rdo rje rnal 'byor mchog gi lha //
NK005(ca)011:429: 'gro drug bdren pa'i dpal lags pas //
NK005(ca)011:430: rin chen can la phyag btsal te //
NK005(ca)011:431: byams mgon khyod la skyabs su mchi //
NK005(ca)011:432: zhes lan gsum gyis phyag bya /
NK005(ca)011:433: drug pa rgyun bshags bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:434: me tog dang bcas pa'i thal mo snyi gar sbyar te /
NK005(ca)011:435: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK005(ca)011:437: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)011:438: sdig pa thams cad so sor bshags //
NK005(ca)011:439: bsod nams kun la yi rang ngo //
NK005(ca)011:440: sangs rgyas byang chub yid kyis bzung //
NK005(ca)011:441: dge ba kun la rjes su smon //
NK005(ca)011:442: byang chub mchog gi sems ni bskyed par bgyi //
NK005(ca)011:443: sems can thams cad bdag gis mgron du gnyer //
NK005(ca)011:444: byang chub spyod mchog yid 'ong spyad par bgyi //
NK005(ca)011:445: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK005(ca)011:446: ces lan gsum gyis rgyun bshags bya /
NK005(ca)011:447: bdun pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:448: slob ma'i snying gar ma las nyi ma'i steng du
NK005(ca)011:449: h+aum las rdo rje rtse dgu pa h+aum yig bskal
NK005(ca)011:450: pa'i me ltar 'bar bas mtshan pa las 'od 'phros
NK005(ca)011:451: / nye bar len pa'i zag bcas kyi phung po ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis bsregs /
NK005(ca)011:452: rnam shes skad cig ma'i rgyun mar me ltar gnas pa la /
NK005(ca)011:453: slob dpon gyis gsang sngags brjod bzhin du spros te
NK005(ca)011:454: bstims pas dpal khrag 'thung chen po yum dang bcas
NK005(ca)011:455: pa'i skur gyur nas snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang sems
NK005(ca)011:456: a yig dmar po zla ba ltar gang ba zung
NK005(ca)011:457: du gyur pa'i 'od kyis lus kyi nyes pa thams
NK005(ca)011:458: cad yongs su dag par bsam la /
NK005(ca)011:459: las bum gyi chus bsang bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:460: brgyad pa dam la bzhag pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:461: rdo rje spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK005(ca)011:463: nges deng khyod de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su bskyed cing /
NK005(ca)011:464: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i ngo bor gnas par byas zin pas /
NK005(ca)011:465: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub
NK005(ca)011:466: kyang thob par gyur zin na thun mong gi dngos
NK005(ca)011:467: grub phal pa thob par lta smos kyang ci dgos
NK005(ca)011:468: pas / khyod kyis dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba su la yang ma smra zhig /
NK005(ca)011:469: gal te smras na khyod dam tshig 'gal bar 'gyur ro //
NK005(ca)011:470: zhes phan yon gyi sgo nas dam la bzhag /
NK005(ca)011:471: dung chen bdud rtsis gang ba bzung nas rdo rje snying gar bzhag ste /
NK005(ca)011:472: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag nyid ni //
NK005(ca)011:473: khyod kyi snying la rab tu gnas //
NK005(ca)011:474: gal te tshul 'di smras gyur na //
NK005(ca)011:475: rdo rje ye shes 'od zer gyis //
NK005(ca)011:476: bsad nas sems can dmyal bar skye //
NK005(ca)011:478: 'di ni dmyal ba'i chu yin te //
NK005(ca)011:479: khyod kyi snying la kun tu gnas //
NK005(ca)011:480: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK005(ca)011:482: gzhan du dam tshig mi 'gyur te //
NK005(ca)011:483: dngos grub nyid du'ang mi 'gyur ro //
NK005(ca)011:484: sngags rnams kun gyi dam tshig ni //
NK005(ca)011:486: zhes nyes dmigs kyii sgo nas dam la bzhag /
NK005(ca)011:487: dung chen gyi bdud rtsi blud la /
NK005(ca)011:488: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK005(ca)011:489: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK005(ca)011:490: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub thob //
NK005(ca)011:492: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK005(ca)011:493: i dan+te na ra kan sarba pa ti hri da ya h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK005(ca)011:494: zhes phan yon dang nyes dmigs gnyis ka'i sgo nas dam la bzhag /
NK005(ca)011:495: sems dpa' rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag nas /
NK005(ca)011:496: rigs kyi bu khyod kyi phyag na rdo rje nga yin gyi //
NK005(ca)011:497: phyin chad ngas ji ltar smras pa de bzhin du byos shig /
NK005(ca)011:498: nga'i bka' las 'das bar ma byed cig /
NK005(ca)011:499: gal te 'das na khyod dus ma yin par 'chi
NK005(ca)011:500: ba'i dus byas nas dmyal bar skye bar 'gyur ta
NK005(ca)011:501: re / zhes bka' gnyan pa'i sgo na sa dam la bzhag go //
NK005(ca)011:502: dgu pa ye shes dbab pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:504: bdag la rdo rje khrag 'thung chen po dbab par mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:506: slob dpon gyi sems ma rdo rje ma'i phyag rgya de'i snying gar bcings te /
NK005(ca)011:507: 'di ni dam tshig khro bo ste //
NK005(ca)011:509: bla med ye shes rdo rje lha //
NK005(ca)011:510: khyod la de ring dbab par bya //
NK005(ca)011:512: slob ma lus drang por bsrangs te gnas pa'i snying
NK005(ca)011:513: gar ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bskal pa'i me
NK005(ca)011:514: ltar 'bar ba'i steng du h+aum las khro bo rdo
NK005(ca)011:515: rje h+aum gis mtshan par bsam nas /
NK005(ca)011:516: g.yon pa'i khu tshur kha sbub pa'i srin lag g.yas
NK005(ca)011:517: pa'i mdzub mos drangs pa rdo rje dbab pa'i rgya
NK005(ca)011:518: bcings te / badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK005(ca)011:519: zhes brjod pas dpal chen po he ru ka sku
NK005(ca)011:520: mdog dang cha lugs ji lta ba bzhin sad par
NK005(ca)011:521: gyur pa la / bla ma'i snying ga'i 'od kyis
NK005(ca)011:522: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dpa' bo rnal
NK005(ca)011:523: 'byor ma'i tshogs thams cad kha char bu yug 'tshubs
NK005(ca)011:524: pa bzhin spyan drangs te slob ma'i snying gar thim
NK005(ca)011:525: gyur pa la / par bsam zhing / spos chen gyis bdug /
NK005(ca)011:526: d+aa dril sogs rol mo sna tshogs pa'i sgra dang sbyar te /
NK005(ca)011:527: ru lu'i mthar ye shes dbab pa'i sngags btags pa drag tu bazla'o //
NK005(ca)011:528: babs pa'i rtags lus 'phar zhing g.yo ba dang /
NK005(ca)011:530: mngon par shes pa 'char ba la sogs pa 'byung zhing /
NK005(ca)011:531: de nyid brtag par byas nas snang ba dris te lung bstan par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:532: bcu pa me tog 'bul ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:533: sngon tshe tshe rabs grangs med nas //
NK005(ca)011:534: dge ba'i las kyis bsten pa'i lha //
NK005(ca)011:535: lhag pa'i lha ni gang yin par //
NK005(ca)011:536: da lta nyid du 'bab par shog /
NK005(ca)011:537: badz+ra pra ti gri h+na h+aum /
NK005(ca)011:540: zhes brjod nas dkyil 'khor du me tog dor zhing /
NK005(ca)011:541: lha gang la babs pa de yi dam du byin nas /
NK005(ca)011:542: me tog de nyid lha de'i sngags dang /
NK005(ca)011:543: rat+na m+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NK005(ca)011:544: zhes pas mgo bor bcings nas lha de slob ma la dbyer med du bstim /
NK005(ca)011:545: bcu gcig pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:546: yi ge bris byin gyis brlabs pa'i gser gyi thur ma bzung la /
NK005(ca)011:547: slob ma'i mig gnyis la yang yi ge pra bsam nas /
NK005(ca)011:548: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK005(ca)011:549: gser gyi thur ma thogs nas ni //
NK005(ca)011:550: 'jig rten ling thog bsal ba ltar //
NK005(ca)011:551: bu khyod mi shes rmongs pa yi //
NK005(ca)011:552: ling thog rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK005(ca)011:553: badz+ra ni tra a pa ha ra pa ta lam hri /
NK005(ca)011:554: shes bya'i sgrib pa bsal nas shes rab kyi mig thob par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)011:555: badz+ra tsak+shu ka ma la sarba su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)011:556: zhes brjod cing gdong g.yogs bkrol /
NK005(ca)011:557: bcu gnyis pa mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:558: slob ma'i mig gnyis la rdo rje bsam nas /
NK005(ca)011:559: de ring rigs kyi bu khyod kyi //
NK005(ca)011:560: rtsol ba'i sems stobs ma chung bar //
NK005(ca)011:562: ye shes dkyil 'khor gzugs brnyan ni //
NK005(ca)011:563: kun rdzob gzugs su bstan pa yin //
NK005(ca)011:564: 'di la dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK005(ca)011:565: rtse gcig yid kyis gnas bgyis la //
NK005(ca)011:566: sems ni gzhan du ma yengs na //
NK005(ca)011:567: dngos grub gzhan du mi 'gyur te //
NK005(ca)011:568: 'on kyang sangs rgyas rigs su skye //
NK005(ca)011:569: sangs rgyas dngos su da gyur te //
NK005(ca)011:570: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs //
NK005(ca)011:571: 'byor pa thams cad mngon du gyur //
NK005(ca)011:572: rten dang dgos grub thams cad kyang //
NK005(ca)011:573: khyod la mngon du phyogs 'gyur bas //
NK005(ca)011:574: dngos grub bsgrub phyir dam tshig srungs //
NK005(ca)011:575: gsang sngags la yang brtson par gyis //
NK005(ca)011:578: gzhal yas khang 'di ni ye shes kyi rnam par 'phrul pa las grub pa ste /
NK005(ca)011:579: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun
NK005(ca)011:580: dang ldan pa'i rtags su gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta
NK005(ca)011:581: babs brgyad la sogs pa gzhal yas khang gi tshad
NK005(ca)011:582: dang mtshan nyid thams cad rdzogs par snang ba'o //
NK005(ca)011:583: khyad par sku gsung thugs dang ldan pas thod pa'i phreng ba /
NK005(ca)011:584: thabs shes dbyer med pas nyi zla //
NK005(ca)011:585: ye shes bzhi'i don rtogs shing byang chub kyi sems
NK005(ca)011:586: nyon mongs pa dang bag chags kyis ma gos par
NK005(ca)011:587: zla gam dang / thugs rjes thams cad khyab pas rin po che'i bla re dang /
NK005(ca)011:588: 'dod yon lnga la spyod pas na bza' sna tshogs dang /
NK005(ca)011:589: che ba'i yon tan dang thugs rje rgyun mi 'chad pas phreng bas kyang brgyan pa'o //
NK005(ca)011:591: mchog ni yid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK005(ca)011:592: gzhal yas khang brtsegs ye shes te //
NK005(ca)011:594: sgo bzhi dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi //
NK005(ca)011:595: rnam thar brgyad ldan rta babs so //
NK005(ca)011:596: rin chen sgo ste thugs rje'i dang //
NK005(ca)011:597: yang dag spong bzhi ta ra na //
NK005(ca)011:598: dran pa nyer bzhag sgo khyud dang //
NK005(ca)011:599: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i sgo khyams ldan //
NK005(ca)011:600: phreng ba byang chub yan lag bdun //
NK005(ca)011:601: 'phags lam brgyad kyi ka brgyad mdzes //
NK005(ca)011:602: lam gyi ye shes rnga yab dang //
NK005(ca)011:603: nyon mongs gcod 'dzems mu tig phreng //
NK005(ca)011:604: dril bu 'phan dag rlung bskyod pa //
NK005(ca)011:605: shes rab chos sgra sgrogs pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:606: che ba'i yon tan 'dus pa'i rtags //
NK005(ca)011:607: bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i rgyal mtshan dang //
NK005(ca)011:608: rten 'brel mtshan pa'i me long dang //
NK005(ca)011:609: ye shes lnga yi tshon rtsi dang //
NK005(ca)011:610: thod phreng sku gsum thob pa'i rtags //
NK005(ca)011:611: gzhal yas khang mchog brgyan pa'o //
NK005(ca)011:612: de ltar rgyu 'bras rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin gnas kyi dkyil 'khor bstan nas /
NK005(ca)011:613: da ni de la bzhugs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams bstan par bya ste /
NK005(ca)011:614: de yang ye shes chen po lnga'i bdag nyid phung
NK005(ca)011:615: po lnga gnas 'gyur nas thob pa'i sku ni de
NK005(ca)011:616: bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngar snang ba las /
NK005(ca)011:617: sems can nyon mongs pa lnga'i mur thug pa /
NK005(ca)011:618: zhi bas 'dul bar mi spyod pa /
NK005(ca)011:619: gdug cing gtum pa rnams 'dul ba'i phyir he ru ka rigs lngar bzhengs pa las /
NK005(ca)011:620: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo rdo
NK005(ca)011:621: rje'i rigs kyi khro bo dpal khrag 'thung gi dkyil
NK005(ca)011:622: 'khor mtha' yas par bstan pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:623: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu dang /
NK005(ca)011:624: khro tshul drug cu rtsa bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK005(ca)011:629: rmad du mtshan ma gsum sogs /
NK005(ca)011:630: byung ba'i chos rnam pa gsum gyis brgyan pa sku mdog dang /
NK005(ca)011:632: rgyan dang cha lugs rnams cir yang snang ba las /
NK005(ca)011:633: 'dir ni rigs kyi dbang gi dbu gsum phyag drug
NK005(ca)011:634: par bstan pa ste sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba
NK005(ca)011:635: chen po'i 'od zer can zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs
NK005(ca)011:636: bzhi pa / g.yas zhal dkar po 'dzum pa /
NK005(ca)011:637: g.yon zhal dmar po gshe ba /
NK005(ca)011:638: dbus zhal mthing nag khros pa'i nyams can /
NK005(ca)011:639: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gsum gsum dang ldan pa /
NK005(ca)011:640: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK005(ca)011:641: ljags 'dril la phata kyi rkan sgra sdeb cing shangs nas h+aum sgra 'byin pa /
NK005(ca)011:642: smin mtshams nas khro gnyer g.yo ba /
NK005(ca)011:643: sma ra dang smin ma'i glog 'od 'khyug cing /
NK005(ca)011:644: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'bar ba /
NK005(ca)011:645: nyi ma bye ba'i gzi mdangs can /
NK005(ca)011:646: sgeg pa la sogs pa gar gyi nyams dgus rgyas pa /
NK005(ca)011:647: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu /
NK005(ca)011:648: bar pa gnyis kyi kha t+w+aam ka dang thod pa khrag gis gang ba /
NK005(ca)011:649: tha ma gnyis kyis thod pa'i rnge'u chung dang /
NK005(ca)011:650: rgyu ma'i zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK005(ca)011:651: zhabs bzhi g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyi rol pa /
NK005(ca)011:652: thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
NK005(ca)011:653: thod rlon gyi do shal dang /
NK005(ca)011:654: thod tshal sbrul rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK005(ca)011:655: zhing lpags dang glang po che'i ko bas stod g.yogs shing /
NK005(ca)011:656: stag lpags kyi sham thabs grol ba /
NK005(ca)011:657: khrag zhag thal ba'i mtshan ma sogs dur khrod chen po'i chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)011:658: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma sngo skya g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK005(ca)011:660: gcer bu lang tsho rgyas pa'i 'jo sgeg can /
NK005(ca)011:661: zhabs g.yas brkyang ba'i rol pas yab dang gnyis su
NK005(ca)011:662: med par sbyor ba ye shes kyi me dpung rab
NK005(ca)011:663: tu 'bar zhing 'khrug pa'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK005(ca)011:664: 'di'i ye shes kyi rang rtsal 'khor gyi khro mo brgyad du shar ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:665: shar du dkar mo mthing ka g.yas zhing dbyug 'phyar zhing /
NK005(ca)011:667: lhor rkun mo ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa'i rtse mo gtso bo'i thugs kar gtod pa /
NK005(ca)011:668: nub tu spos mo dmar mo g.yas chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan dang g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)011:669: byang du rmongs mo mthing nag g.yas rdo rje rgya gram 'phyar zhing /
NK005(ca)011:670: g.yon zhing chung gi dbyug pa g.yob pa /
NK005(ca)011:671: shar lhor rgan byed ma dmar ser g.yon zhing chung
NK005(ca)011:672: bzung ba'i rgyu ma g.yas pas 'dren cing stob pa
NK005(ca)011:673: / lho nub tu thal byed ma ljang nag g.yas
NK005(ca)011:674: pa'i rdo rjes g.yon gyi dung khrag dkrug cing gsol
NK005(ca)011:675: / ba / nub byang du ma tshogs ma mthing
NK005(ca)011:676: nag phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas snying za ba
NK005(ca)011:677: / ba / / byang shar du dur khrod ma
NK005(ca)011:678: ser skya g.yon zhing chung bzung ba'i mgo bo g.yas
NK005(ca)011:680: de thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK005(ca)011:682: gcer bu dur khrod rol pa'i chas can g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis zhing gi stan la rol pa'o //
NK005(ca)011:683: de ltar sku phyag rgya'i mtshan nyid tha dad par snang yang /
NK005(ca)011:684: ye shes dang rang bzhin gzhan du 'gyur ba med cing /
NK005(ca)011:685: chos kyi sku las g.yo ba med par shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:687: yul can ye shes 'dus pa'i ngo bo ni sh+r+ai he ru ka'o //
NK005(ca)011:688: yul chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo ni yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma'o //
NK005(ca)011:689: rnam par shes pa brgyad kyi ngo bo ni go r+ai ma khro mo brgyad do //
NK005(ca)011:690: de'i yul la sogs pa ni seng+ha phra men brgyad do //
NK005(ca)011:691: rgyan gyi lha mo dang dbang phyug ma la sogs
NK005(ca)011:692: pa de dag gi byin rlabs kyi cho 'phrul shar
NK005(ca)011:693: ba'o // de rnams rnam pa tha dad par snang yang /
NK005(ca)011:694: don dbyings dang ye shes las mi g.yo ba ni don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK005(ca)011:695: rtags thabs dang shes rab kyi tshul du snang ba ni kun rdzob bden pa'i tshul du snang ba'o //
NK005(ca)011:696: zhes sogs rgyas bsdus skabs dang 'tshams par 'chad cing /
NK005(ca)011:697: gzhan du 'dir rten dang brten pa'i rnam pa tsam
NK005(ca)011:698: bstan nas de nyid brjod pa gdod dbang bskur nas
NK005(ca)011:699: bya'o zhes bshad kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges so
NK005(ca)011:700: // de dag ni dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga'o //
NK005(ca)011:701: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba dngos la /
NK005(ca)011:705: rdzogs pa'i dbang dang bzhi las /
NK005(ca)011:706: dang po la sngon 'gro'i yan lag dang /
NK005(ca)011:707: dngos gzhi'i dbang gnyis las dang po ni /
NK005(ca)011:708: man+dala phul nas me tog dang bcas pa'i thal mo sbyar bas btud de /
NK005(ca)011:709: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas kyis //
NK005(ca)011:710: ji ltar mchod chen bgyis pa ltar //
NK005(ca)011:711: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral slad du //
NK005(ca)011:712: nam mkha'i rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)011:713: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab pa la /
NK005(ca)011:715: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK005(ca)011:716: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:717: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK005(ca)011:718: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK005(ca)011:719: zhes phan yon gyi spro ba bskyed nas /
NK005(ca)011:720: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi rgyal ba nam mkha'i dbyings gang bar bzhugs pa la /
NK005(ca)011:721: bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi gtso bo rnams kyis
NK005(ca)011:722: bdag dang slob mar bcas pa la ye shes bla
NK005(ca)011:723: na med pa'i dbang bskur du gsol /
NK005(ca)011:724: zhes slob dpon gyis nam mkha'i lha la gsol ba btab pas /
NK005(ca)011:725: de rnams kyis gdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan la sogs pas phyogs kun khyab par bres /
NK005(ca)011:726: dung dang rnga bo che dang rgyud mngas la sogs pa rol mo sna tshogs snyan par bsgrags /
NK005(ca)011:727: bkra shis pa'i glu dbyangs rnam pa du ma dang
NK005(ca)011:728: ldan pas dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab par bsam
NK005(ca)011:729: mo // gnyis pa dbang dngos la bcu bdun las /
NK005(ca)011:730: dang po sku gsung thugs rdo rjer dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:731: slob ma'i spyi mgrin snying gar zla ba pad+ma nyi ma la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK005(ca)011:733: h+aum sngon po rnams 'od 'bar bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)011:736: las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pa rang 'dra'i spyan ma dang sbyor ba /
NK005(ca)011:737: de las rnam snang yab yum dpag med spros nam mkha' gang bar bzhugs pa la /
NK005(ca)011:738: dpal ldan rdo rje'i sku 'chang ba //
NK005(ca)011:739: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms pas //
NK005(ca)011:740: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK005(ca)011:741: rdo rje'i sku yir mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:743: nam mkha'i rnam snang yab yum spyi bor rnam snang la thim /
NK005(ca)011:744: de las 'od zer byung bas lus thams cad khyab /
NK005(ca)011:745: lus kyi bag chags byang zhing dag nas mtshan dpes
NK005(ca)011:746: brgyan pa'i ye shes kyi sku gyur par bsam zhing
NK005(ca)011:747: // phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK005(ca)011:748: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms pas //
NK005(ca)011:749: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK005(ca)011:750: rdo rje'i sku yir mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:751: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)011:753: sku rdo rjer dbang thob par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:755: a mi de wa h+r+aih zhes brjod pas /
NK005(ca)011:756: +aahls snang ba mtha' yas dmar po pad+ma dang dril
NK005(ca)011:757: bu 'dzin pa rang 'dra'i gos dkar mo dang sbyor
NK005(ca)011:758: ba / de las snang ba mtha' yas yab yum
NK005(ca)011:759: dpag med spros nam mkha' gang bar bzhugs pa la
NK005(ca)011:761: chos kyi ngag lam dpal dang ldan //
NK005(ca)011:762: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms pas //
NK005(ca)011:763: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK005(ca)011:764: rdo rje'i gsung gir mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:765: zhes gsol ba btab pas nam mkha'i snang mtha' yab yum mgrin pa'i snang mtha' la thim /
NK005(ca)011:766: de las 'od zer byung bas ngag gi bag chags
NK005(ca)011:767: byang zhing dag nas gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu
NK005(ca)011:768: dang ldan pa'i ye shes kyi gsung du gyur par
NK005(ca)011:769: bsam zhing / +aah phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK005(ca)011:770: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms pas //
NK005(ca)011:771: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK005(ca)011:772: rdo rje'i gsung gir mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:773: sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)011:774: zhes gsung rdo rjer dbang thob par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:775: snying ga'i h+aum la dmigs te /
NK005(ca)011:778: mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo rje dang dril bu
NK005(ca)011:779: 'dzin pa rang 'dra'i m+aa ma k+ai dang sbyor ba
NK005(ca)011:780: / de las mi bskyod pa yab yum dpag med spros /
NK005(ca)011:781: nam mkha' gang bar bzhugs pa la /
NK005(ca)011:782: dpal ldan thugs kyi rdo rje 'chang //
NK005(ca)011:783: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms pas //
NK005(ca)011:784: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK005(ca)011:785: rdo rje'i thugs kyir mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:786: zhes gsol ba btab pas nam mkha'i mi bskyod pa yab yum snying ga'i mi bskyod pa la thim /
NK005(ca)011:787: de las 'od zer byung bas yid kyi bag chags
NK005(ca)011:788: byang zhing dag nas sems nyid de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK005(ca)011:789: thugs ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i thugs su gyur
NK005(ca)011:790: par bsam zhing / phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK005(ca)011:791: rdo rjee mi phyed gsum bsgoms pas //
NK005(ca)011:792: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK005(ca)011:793: rdo rje'i thugs su mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:794: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swab+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)011:796: thugs rdo rjer dbang thob par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:797: gnyis pa bum pa'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:798: snying ga'i h+aum gi 'od zer gyis bskul bas /
NK005(ca)011:799: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la bzhugs pa'i rigs lnga'i sangs
NK005(ca)011:800: rgyas yab yum rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i byang
NK005(ca)011:801: sems bdud rtsis gang ba'i bum pa spyan ma la
NK005(ca)011:802: sogs pa'i lha mos bzung ste spyi bo nas dbang
NK005(ca)011:803: bskur bas byang chub sems kyi rdul phra rab kyis
NK005(ca)011:804: lus thams cad gang bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)011:805: chos dbyings yum gyi bum pa na //
NK005(ca)011:806: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor pho brang bzhugs //
NK005(ca)011:807: gnyis med byang chub sems brtags chus //
NK005(ca)011:808: spyi nas bstim zhing dbang bskur bas //
NK005(ca)011:809: lus la sangs rgyas gtams par shog /
NK005(ca)011:810: bud+d+ha ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK005(ca)011:815: zhes sbyar ba brjod bzhin du mgo bo'i gnas lngar bskur zhing bum chu blud /
NK005(ca)011:816: de ltar dbang bskur bas nye bar len pa'i phung
NK005(ca)011:817: po zag pa dang bcas pa'i dri ma dag nas
NK005(ca)011:818: ye shes kyi lus zag pa med pa'i sku dang
NK005(ca)011:819: ldan pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:821: gsum pa dbu rgyan gyi dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:822: rigs lnga yab yum bcu snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang
NK005(ca)011:823: sems mgo bo'i gnas lngar thim pas lus thams cad
NK005(ca)011:825: thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan dang //
NK005(ca)011:826: sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu can //
NK005(ca)011:827: kun nas nyon mongs 'jig rten dbang //
NK005(ca)011:828: mi phyed la sogs de 'grub pas //
NK005(ca)011:829: ye shes lnga ldan dbu rgyan 'dis //
NK005(ca)011:830: khyod la dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK005(ca)011:831: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)011:838: dbang bskur bas sku lnga'i 'od zer gyis dug lnga'i
NK005(ca)011:839: nyes pa byang zhing dag nas 'gro ba yongs kyi
NK005(ca)011:840: dpal mgon du 'gyur ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK005(ca)011:841: / bzhi pa cod pan gyi dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:843: ras kyi cod pan sngo dmar zheng du khru gang /
NK005(ca)011:844: srid du khru bcu gnyis kyi tshad dang ldan pa mgo bor bcings te /
NK005(ca)011:845: bag chags nyes pa'i skyon bral zhing //
NK005(ca)011:846: 'khor ba'i nyes pas mi gos pa'i //
NK005(ca)011:847: ye shes lnga ldan cod pan 'dis //
NK005(ca)011:848: khyod la dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK005(ca)011:849: badz+ra pa ta lam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih zhi gnas
NK005(ca)011:850: dang lhag mthong zung du 'brel zhing shes bya la
NK005(ca)011:851: thogs pa med pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:852: lnga pa phreng ba'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:853: me tog dang rin po che'i phreng ba'am /
NK005(ca)011:854: mi mgo'i phreng ba skra mtshams su bcings te /
NK005(ca)011:855: 'di ni rin chen phreng ba ste /
NK005(ca)011:856: rin chen rgyu las byas pa yis //
NK005(ca)011:857: byang chub yan lag phreng ba 'dis //
NK005(ca)011:859: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:860: bar chad med par dbang bskur ro //
NK005(ca)011:861: badz+ra rat+na m+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK005(ca)011:862: 'phags pa mchod pa dang 'gro ba'i don byed pa
NK005(ca)011:863: la bar chad med cing bsam pa yid bzhin du
NK005(ca)011:864: 'grub pa dang / byang chub kyi yan lag bdun
NK005(ca)011:865: gyi ngo bo nyid du 'gyur ba'i dbang thob par
NK005(ca)011:866: 'grub pa dang / gyur cig / drug pa phyag rgya'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:867: me tog gang la babs pa'i lha de'i phyag rgya bzhi lus la bkod /
NK005(ca)011:868: dam rgya snying gar gtugs la /
NK005(ca)011:870: phyag rgya 'dis ni dbang bskur bas //
NK005(ca)011:871: chos rnams sku gsung thugs kyi ngang //
NK005(ca)011:872: phyag rgya chen po'i rang bzhin du //
NK005(ca)011:873: rtag tu bsgom zhing bsgrub par gyis //
NK005(ca)011:874: bud+d+ha mu dra a b+hi shiny+tsa ah zhes dang lha
NK005(ca)011:875: gang yin de'i sngags la mu dra sogs btags te
NK005(ca)011:876: dbang bskur bas / sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK005(ca)011:877: las mi 'gyur ba rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i phyag
NK005(ca)011:878: rgya dang ldan pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:880: rigs bzang gi thod pa s+w+aa'am t+r+aam bris pa rin po ches gtams pa gtad la /
NK005(ca)011:882: chos nyid spros bral rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK005(ca)011:883: sku lnga lhun rdzogs rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK005(ca)011:884: ye shes lnga ldan rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK005(ca)011:885: sku gsum ldan pa'i rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK005(ca)011:886: mi 'gyur g.yung drung rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK005(ca)011:887: yid bzhin gter ldan rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK005(ca)011:888: skal ldan khyod la dbang 'di bskur ba yis //
NK005(ca)011:889: ci bsam 'grub pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK005(ca)011:891: de ba rat+na tree lokya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK005(ca)011:892: de las 'od zer 'phros slob bu'i dri ma sbyangs 'od kyi gong bur gyur pa las lhar bskyed /
NK005(ca)011:893: b+hany+dza yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i dbang
NK005(ca)011:894: bskur bas yid la ci bsam pa thams cad 'grub
NK005(ca)011:895: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:896: brgyad pa rdo rje dang dril bu'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:897: h+aum dang +aa las rdo rje dang dril bu gar
NK005(ca)011:898: stabs su bskor nas slob bu'i lag pa gnyis su
NK005(ca)011:899: gtad la / nyon mongs 'joms pa'i rdo rje dang //
NK005(ca)011:900: chos sgra sgrogs pa'i dril bu 'dis //
NK005(ca)011:901: de ring khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK005(ca)011:902: thabs dang shes rab 'phel bar shog /
NK005(ca)011:903: badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+ny+ao pa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK005(ca)011:905: dbang bskur bas don dbyings dang ye shes tha mi
NK005(ca)011:906: dad pa'i rtags thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel
NK005(ca)011:907: ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:908: dgu pa 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:909: gzugs sogs bud med lha mo'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)011:910: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan dag /
NK005(ca)011:911: chos nyid kyi ni rgyan yin pas //
NK005(ca)011:912: dga' mgur spyod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK005(ca)011:913: na mo ha ra gu na pany+tsa a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK005(ca)011:914: zhes dbang bskur te theg pa 'og ma pas bkag pa'ang gsang sngags kyi dang du blangs te /
NK005(ca)011:915: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mor dmigs nas spyad
NK005(ca)011:916: par ye shes chen po chos kyi dbyings la 'jug
NK005(ca)011:917: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:918: bcu pa bdun rtsi rnam pa lnga'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:919: dpa' bo 'bru lngas byin gyis brlabs pa'i bdud rtsi'i thod pa gtad la /
NK005(ca)011:920: b+hany+dza bcud yangs zab pa ni //
NK005(ca)011:921: 'khor yug gtogs pa'i snod bcud kun //
NK005(ca)011:922: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin yin pas na //
NK005(ca)011:923: rtag tu za byed zhal du bstim //
NK005(ca)011:924: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum a /
NK005(ca)011:925: zhes pas g.yon pas mtheb srin la nyi zla'i steng
NK005(ca)011:926: du h+r+aihyiga bsam pas bdud rtsi blangs pa slob ma'i
NK005(ca)011:927: gnas gsum du thig le byas nas khar blud pas
NK005(ca)011:928: lus kyi lha thams cad tshim par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)011:929: bdag dang gzhan gyi rnam par rtog pa sbyong zhing /
NK005(ca)011:930: mchog dang thun mong gis bsdus pa'i dngos grub 'grub pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:931: bcu gcig pa lcags kyu rnam pa lnga'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:932: yum lnga'i yi ge 'bru lngas byin gyis brlabs pa'i dam rdzas kyi thod pa gtad la /
NK005(ca)011:933: mngon shes lnga la sogs pa yi //
NK005(ca)011:934: thun mong dngos grub ji snyed dang //
NK005(ca)011:935: rig 'dzin gtso bor sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)011:936: lcags kyu lnga yis dbang bskur ro //
NK005(ca)011:937: +aahh+aum ma h+aa m+aam sa pany+tsa a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK005(ca)011:942: rig 'dzin gyi gtso bo la sogs pa 'grub par byed pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:943: bcu gnyis pa ming gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:944: gang la babs pa'i lha de'i rigs dang mthun pa'i ming btags la /
NK005(ca)011:945: 'di ni rdo rje ming gi dbang //
NK005(ca)011:946: mtshan mchog 'dis ni dbang bskur bas //
NK005(ca)011:947: sangs rgyas zhing du grags pa yi //
NK005(ca)011:951: zhes ming gi dbang bskur bas zhing khams kun tu
NK005(ca)011:952: grags pa chos kyi rgyal po chen po'i dbang thob
NK005(ca)011:953: par gyur cig / bcu gsum pa sgrub rdzas lha cha lnga'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:954: zhing gi rgyal mtshan rigs gnyis /
NK005(ca)011:957: sprin chen gyi bla re rnams bsgrags tshig rgyas pa gzhan du 'byung ba bzhin nam /
NK005(ca)011:959: zhing lpags rgyal mtshan gnyis dang ro ras 'phan //
NK005(ca)011:960: g.yang gzhi'i ba dan sprin chen bla re ste //
NK005(ca)011:961: sgrub rdzas lha cha lnga yi dbang bskur bas //
NK005(ca)011:962: nyon mongs g.yul bzlog dpal chen mthu thob shog /
NK005(ca)011:963: ces nyon mongs pa'i g.yul ngo bzlog cing bdud kyi
NK005(ca)011:964: dmag tshogs las rgyal ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK005(ca)011:965: / bcu bzhi pa kha t+w+aam ka'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:967: rdo rje kha t+w+aam 'di byin pas //
NK005(ca)011:968: dril bu'i sgra ni gsil ba yis //
NK005(ca)011:969: thams cad phab nas slar yang ni //
NK005(ca)011:970: khams gsum dag kyang 'tsho bar byed //
NK005(ca)011:971: badz+ra kha t+w+aam g+han+de a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK005(ca)011:973: 'jig rten gsum po dag 'jig cing slar 'tsho bar byed pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:974: bco lnga pa phur bu'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:975: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs shing bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i phur bu gtad la /
NK005(ca)011:977: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras kyi mchog /
NK005(ca)011:978: sku gsung thugs su byin brlabs te //
NK005(ca)011:979: dgra bgegs 'joms pa'i mthu mnga' ba'i //
NK005(ca)011:980: phur bu 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK005(ca)011:981: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+hana bam h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)011:983: zhes lag pa byin gyis brlabs pas 'dril du gzhug /
NK005(ca)011:984: ces rmad du byung ba'i phrin las kyis gdug pa
NK005(ca)011:985: can gtan 'pho bar byed cing khams gsum sgrol ba'i
NK005(ca)011:987: bcu drug pa tshe dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:989: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid kyi //
NK005(ca)011:990: rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang dpal //
NK005(ca)011:991: de ring khyod la dbang bskur gyi //
NK005(ca)011:992: nang med bde mchog grub par shog /
NK005(ca)011:993: +aa yu pun+d+yee pun+d+yee ma h+aa pun+d+yee ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)011:996: rgas rgud kyi sdug bsngal bsal te tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)011:997: ces sogs smon lam btab pa'i don de dang de thob par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:998: bcu bdun pa rgyal po bka' rtags kyi dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:1005: bkra shis rdzas brgyad rnams kyi dbang ste spro na gzhan du 'byung ba bzhin bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:1006: de ltar dbang bcu bdun po ni rdo rje theg
NK005(ca)011:1007: pa'i rgyud lung man ngag kun las bsdus pa ste
NK005(ca)011:1008: / rdo rje'i tshul du dbang yang sbyin //
NK005(ca)011:1010: de ltar phyi gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du bum
NK005(ca)011:1011: pa la sogs pa phyi'i rdzas la brten nas dbang
NK005(ca)011:1012: bskur bas / lus kyi dri ma dag nas sa brgyad pa'i byang sems dang skal pa mnyam zhing /
NK005(ca)011:1013: snang srid lha'i 'khor lor rtogs pas /
NK005(ca)011:1014: las dang bya ba la rmongs pa med par 'jug pa dang /
NK005(ca)011:1015: zhugs pas bdag don grub nas gzhan la phan par byed pas phan pa'i dbang zhes bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:1016: gnyis pa nang gi dbang bskur ba la bzhi las /
NK005(ca)011:1017: dang po 'dod don gsol ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:1018: slob ma'i ma da na'i skyems dang /
NK005(ca)011:1019: gser la sogs pa'i me tog gis mchod cing rig ma mtshan dang ldan pa phul la /
NK005(ca)011:1020: phyag dang man+dala sngon du 'gro bas thal mo sbyar te /
NK005(ca)011:1021: ji ltar dus gsum rgyal ba yis //
NK005(ca)011:1022: dam chos bdud rtsi'i char phabs pas //
NK005(ca)011:1023: skal ldan 'gro ba'i rgyud sbyangs shing //
NK005(ca)011:1024: skal med kun gyi skyabs mdzad ltar //
NK005(ca)011:1025: de ring rdo rje slob dpon gyi //
NK005(ca)011:1026: zhabs la btud de zhu ba ni //
NK005(ca)011:1027: bdag gi rgyud rnams sbyang ba dang //
NK005(ca)011:1028: 'gro ba rnams la phan don du //
NK005(ca)011:1029: sngon gyi rgyal bas mdzad pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)011:1030: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:1031: zhes gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK005(ca)011:1033: khyod nyid brtse bas bzung ba dang //
NK005(ca)011:1034: 'gro kun byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)011:1035: dpal ldan bla ma bdag nyid kyis //
NK005(ca)011:1036: khyod la dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK005(ca)011:1038: gnyis pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:1041: mdzes pa'i rgyan dang ldan pa g.yon du bzhag la /
NK005(ca)011:1042: rang nyid skad cig gis dpal chen po he ru kar gsal ba dang /
NK005(ca)011:1043: yum gyi snying gar yi ge a dkar po /
NK005(ca)011:1044: de las 'od zer 'phros pas nyer len gyi phung po bsregs shing sbyang nas gzhi'i a la thim /
NK005(ca)011:1045: de yang je chung je phrar yal te mi dmigs
NK005(ca)011:1046: pa las h+aum zhes brjod pas h+aum mthing nag tshon
NK005(ca)011:1047: gang bar gyur / de 'phros shing 'dus pa las
NK005(ca)011:1048: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma'i skur gyur pa las
NK005(ca)011:1049: gang bar gyur / / yab kyi spyi bo la
NK005(ca)011:1050: sogs pa'i gnas lngar rnam snang sogs rgyal ba yab
NK005(ca)011:1051: lnga rigs kyi sems dpa' bzhi bzhis bskor ba dang
NK005(ca)011:1052: gang bar gyur / / / yan lag bzhi la khro bo bzhi /
NK005(ca)011:1053: yum gyi spyi bo la sogs pa'i gnas lngar dbyings
NK005(ca)011:1054: phyug ma sogs rgyal ba yum lnga rigs kyi sems
NK005(ca)011:1055: ma bzhi bzhis bskor ba dang yan lag bzhi la
NK005(ca)011:1056: sgo ma bzhi gsal btab la /
NK005(ca)011:1057: de ltar yab yum rnams dgyes par rol pa'i dga'
NK005(ca)011:1058: ba'i rol mos rang bzhin lhun grub kyi rgyal ba
NK005(ca)011:1060: mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa la phyag mchod kyi dgyes par byas pas /
NK005(ca)011:1061: lha yab la yab dang yum la yum gnyis med du thim par bsam /
NK005(ca)011:1062: gsum pa sbyor ba brtsam pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:1063: de nas yab kyi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum chad yum
NK005(ca)011:1064: gyi mkhar thim pas zla gam dmar po'i dbus su
NK005(ca)011:1065: pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i zer 'brur zla ba la
NK005(ca)011:1066: am dmar pos mtshan par bsam /
NK005(ca)011:1067: yum gyi thugs ka nas h+aum chad /
NK005(ca)011:1068: yab kyi gsang gnas su thim pas rdo rje rtse
NK005(ca)011:1069: lnga pa'i bum par nyi ma la a dkar pos
NK005(ca)011:1071: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)011:1074: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK005(ca)011:1075: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis drangs 'khyud sbyar nas mnyes par byas te /
NK005(ca)011:1077: zhes bskyod nas snyoms par zhugs pas bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)011:1078: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a nu r+aa ga na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)011:1079: zhes pas byang sems am gis bsdus shing h+aum gis
NK005(ca)011:1080: bskul nas phata kyis yum gyi gsang bar babs pas
NK005(ca)011:1081: zla ba lta bur gsal ba'i 'od kyis gzung 'dzin
NK005(ca)011:1082: gyi dri ma sbyangs snod bcud ye shes kyi 'khor
NK005(ca)011:1084: bzhi pa byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:1085: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs
NK005(ca)011:1086: pa thams cad kyi dbang dang byin rlabs thams cad
NK005(ca)011:1087: kyi dbang dang byin rlabs thams cad bsdus mkha' nang
NK005(ca)011:1089: de nyid slob ma'i spyi bo nas bstims pas lus
NK005(ca)011:1090: ngag yid gsum gyi rtog sgrib sbyangs nas h+aum du
NK005(ca)011:1091: gyur / de rdo rjer gyur pa las dpal chen
NK005(ca)011:1092: po'i skur bskyed pa la rdo rje'i ming byin nas
NK005(ca)011:1093: gyur / / bla ma yab yum gyi byang sems
NK005(ca)011:1094: dngos grub kyi snying por gyur pa snod du blugs
NK005(ca)011:1095: gyur / / pa / bdud rtsi lnga dang mngar
NK005(ca)011:1096: gsum sbyar ba cha gsum du bcad pa'i dang po
NK005(ca)011:1098: slob dpon gyi mtheb srin gyi bar du nyi ma la h+r+aihbasama pas blangs te /
NK005(ca)011:1099: slob ma'i mgrin pa pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa mdun
NK005(ca)011:1100: gyi 'dab ma lcer gyur pa'i zla ba la rdo
NK005(ca)011:1101: rje rtse lnga pa h+aum gis mtshan pa la bzhag
NK005(ca)011:1102: cing / ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK005(ca)011:1103: a ho ma h+aa su kha /
NK005(ca)011:1105: slar yang gnas gsum du thig le byas la /
NK005(ca)011:1107: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum zhes brjod cing myang du bcug pas /
NK005(ca)011:1108: lus thams cad khyab sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub
NK005(ca)011:1109: dang de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i
NK005(ca)011:1110: dbang thob cing lus kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad mnyes
NK005(ca)011:1111: par bsam mo // byang sems cha gnyis pas nus
NK005(ca)011:1112: dbang lnga bskur ba la dang po nyan pa'i dbang
NK005(ca)011:1113: par bsam mo // ni / rna bar byang sems kyi thig le byas la /
NK005(ca)011:1114: slob ma'i rna ba'i nang du b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas
NK005(ca)011:1115: khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i
NK005(ca)011:1116: dbus dang phyogs bzhir nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la t+r+aam
NK005(ca)011:1117: mthing zung lnga'i 'phro 'du las rin po cher gyur
NK005(ca)011:1118: / de las rin chen 'byung gnas yab yum la
NK005(ca)011:1119: rin chen rigs kyi sems dpa' bzhi dang sgo ba
NK005(ca)011:1120: bzhi rnams yum dang bcas pas bskor bar gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1121: de rnams snyoms par zhugs te 'od du zhu ba
NK005(ca)011:1122: las rin chen 'byung gnas kyi skur gyur pa la
NK005(ca)011:1123: / badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs /
NK005(ca)011:1124: dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis su med par bstim /
NK005(ca)011:1125: rgyud kyi glegs bam gtad de /
NK005(ca)011:1127: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang //
NK005(ca)011:1128: gsang ba kun la mnyan par bya //
NK005(ca)011:1129: gsang ba'i don nyid brtag pa las //
NK005(ca)011:1130: gzhan du smra bar bya ba min //
NK005(ca)011:1131: zhes pas nyan cing thos pa'i skal pa dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:1132: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:1133: snying gar thig le byas la /
NK005(ca)011:1134: snying gi nang du b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang 'khor
NK005(ca)011:1135: lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i dbus dang
NK005(ca)011:1136: phyogs bzhir nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la h+aum dkar po
NK005(ca)011:1137: zung lnga'i 'phro 'du las rdo rjer gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1138: de las rdo rjee sems dpa' yab yum la rdo
NK005(ca)011:1139: rje rigs kyi sems dpa' bzhi dang sgo ba bzhi
NK005(ca)011:1140: rnams yum dang bcas pas bskor bar gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1141: de rnams snyoms par zhugs te 'od du zhu ba las rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1147: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po //
NK005(ca)011:1148: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK005(ca)011:1149: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod la //
NK005(ca)011:1150: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK005(ca)011:1151: yi dam gyi lha gang bsgrub kyang 'grub pa'i skal pa dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:1152: gsum pa las kyi dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:1153: lag pa g.yas su thig le byas la /
NK005(ca)011:1154: thal steng du b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang 'khor lo
NK005(ca)011:1155: rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i dbus dang phyogs
NK005(ca)011:1156: bzhir nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la h+aa ljang gu zung
NK005(ca)011:1158: de las don grub yab yum la las kyi rigs
NK005(ca)011:1159: kyi sems dpa' bzhi dang sgo ba bzhi rnams yum
NK005(ca)011:1160: dang bcas pas bskor bar gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1161: de rnams snyoms par zhugs te 'od du zhu ba las don yod grub pa'i skur gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1164: rdo rje rgya gram gtad la //
NK005(ca)011:1165: khyod ni rdo rje las yin te //
NK005(ca)011:1166: las rnams ma lus kun gyis shig /
NK005(ca)011:1168: khyod kyi dgos pa byed pa yin //
NK005(ca)011:1169: sangs rgyas rnams kyi phrin las rnam pa bzhi bsgrub pa'i skal pa dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:1171: lce la thig le byas te /
NK005(ca)011:1172: lce'i steng du b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang 'khor lo
NK005(ca)011:1173: rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i dbus dang phyogs
NK005(ca)011:1174: bzhir nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la h+r+aihdamara po zung lnga'i
NK005(ca)011:1176: de las snang mtha' yab yum la pad+ma rigs kyi
NK005(ca)011:1177: sems dpa' bzhi dang sgo ba bzhi rnams yum dang
NK005(ca)011:1179: de rnams snyoms par zhugs te 'od du zhu ba las 'od dpag med kyi skur gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1182: 'khor lo dung dang pusti rnams gtad la //
NK005(ca)011:1183: chos kyi bdud rtsi bla med pas //
NK005(ca)011:1184: dad ldan skyes bu ngoms par byos //
NK005(ca)011:1185: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK005(ca)011:1186: mthun par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min //
NK005(ca)011:1187: theg pa mtha' dag 'chad cing spel ba'i skal ba dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:1188: lnga pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:1189: slob ma'i yan lag lnga la b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas
NK005(ca)011:1190: khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)011:1191: lnga'i dbus dang phyogs bzhir h+aum s+w+aam +aamhh+aam rnams las
NK005(ca)011:1193: de las rgyal ba rigs lnga yab yum rigs kyi
NK005(ca)011:1194: sems dpa'i 'khor dang khro bo bcu yum dang bcas
NK005(ca)011:1195: par gyur / de rnams snyoms par zhugs te 'od
NK005(ca)011:1196: du zhu ba las rigs kyi bdag po'i skur gyur
NK005(ca)011:1197: par gyur / / badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs drangs /
NK005(ca)011:1200: phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)011:1201: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK005(ca)011:1202: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK005(ca)011:1203: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin par spyod //
NK005(ca)011:1204: rdo rje rgyal po'i go 'phang thob pa'i skal pa dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)011:1205: de nas sgrub pa'i dbang bskur ba la /
NK005(ca)011:1206: lha rgyan gcig sgrub pa'i dbang dang /
NK005(ca)011:1207: tshom bu sgrub pa'i dbang ste /
NK005(ca)011:1208: re re'ang khyad par gyi bye brag tha dad pas
NK005(ca)011:1209: bskur bar gsungs pa ni skabs don gyi bye brag
NK005(ca)011:1210: shes pas sbyar bar bya zhing /
NK005(ca)011:1211: de yang slob ma nub sgor zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor du bzhag la /
NK005(ca)011:1212: byang sems cha gsum pas snying gar thig le byas te /
NK005(ca)011:1213: slob bu'i tsit+ta rin po che'i gur khang du dpal
NK005(ca)011:1214: chen po yab yum bskyed pa snyoms par zhugs te
NK005(ca)011:1215: rjes chags kyi mes zhu nas chos kyi dbyings su
NK005(ca)011:1216: thim pa las dpal chen po'i skur gyur /
NK005(ca)011:1217: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs drangs /
NK005(ca)011:1220: thod sku'i b+hany+dza dang mar me rdor dril lag tu gtad la /
NK005(ca)011:1222: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen te //
NK005(ca)011:1223: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK005(ca)011:1225: chos la 'dod bzhin dbang bskur ro //
NK005(ca)011:1226: zhes dang rtsa ba'i snying po brjod nas /
NK005(ca)011:1227: de ltar dpal chen po khyad par du sgrub pa'i
NK005(ca)011:1228: dbang bskur ba 'di rnams khyod kyi thob par gyur
NK005(ca)011:1229: cig / ces brjod cing bsgom mo //
NK005(ca)011:1230: de ltar byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du nang
NK005(ca)011:1231: gi dbang bskur bas ngag gi dri ma dag nas
NK005(ca)011:1232: sa bcu ba'i byang sems dang skal ba mnyam zhing
NK005(ca)011:1233: / 'khor 'das sgyu mar rtogs pas bde mchog gi
NK005(ca)011:1234: ye shes rigs drug gi sku thob nas 'gro ba'i
NK005(ca)011:1236: nyan sgrub las dang 'chad pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:1237: rdo rje rgyal po'i gnas thob cing //
NK005(ca)011:1238: tshom bu sgrub pa la sogs pa //
NK005(ca)011:1239: nus pas nus pa'i dbang zhes bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:1240: gsum pa gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)011:1241: slob mas rdo rje slob dpon la mchod cing phyag dang man+dala sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)011:1242: ji ltar dus gsum rgyal ba yis //
NK005(ca)011:1243: dam chos bdud rtsi'i char phab pas //
NK005(ca)011:1244: skal ldan 'gro ba'i rgyud sbyangs shing //
NK005(ca)011:1245: skal med kun gyi skyabs mdzad ltar //
NK005(ca)011:1246: de ring rdo rje slob dpon gyi //
NK005(ca)011:1247: zhabs la btud de zhu ba ni //
NK005(ca)011:1248: bdag gi rgyud rnams sbyang ba dang //
NK005(ca)011:1249: 'gro ba rnams la phan don du //
NK005(ca)011:1250: sngon gyi rgyal bas mdzad pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)011:1251: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur du gsol //
NK005(ca)011:1252: zhes gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK005(ca)011:1254: khyod nyid brtse bas bzung ba dang //
NK005(ca)011:1255: 'gro kun byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)011:1256: dpal ldan bla ma bdag nyid kyis //
NK005(ca)011:1257: khyod la dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK005(ca)011:1259: slob mas rigs dang mthun pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi rig ma yid du 'ong ba 'du byas la /
NK005(ca)011:1260: slob dpon gyis gzungs ma de'i lag pa nas bzung ste slob ma'i lag tu gtad la /
NK005(ca)011:1261: legs par nyon cig rigs kyi bu //
NK005(ca)011:1262: bde chen go 'phang bsgrub pa la //
NK005(ca)011:1263: shin tu dad ldan shes rab ma //
NK005(ca)011:1264: khyod kyi grogs kyi dam pa sbyin //
NK005(ca)011:1266: de gnyis bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas /
NK005(ca)011:1267: slob ma dpal he ru ka dang /
NK005(ca)011:1268: rig ma khro mo dbang phyug ma'i skur bskyed pa'i gnas lngar rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK005(ca)011:1269: yan lag bzhi la sgo ba yab yum rnams bkod /
NK005(ca)011:1270: yab yum rnams dga' ba'i rol mos rang bzhin gyi rgyal ba rnams spyan drangs /
NK005(ca)011:1273: yum gyi mkha' zla gam dmar po'i dbus su pad+ma
NK005(ca)011:1274: 'dab ma brgyad pa'i ze'u 'brur zla ba la am
NK005(ca)011:1275: dmar po / yab kyi gsang gnas rdo rje rtse
NK005(ca)011:1276: lnga pa'i bum par nyi ma la a dkar pos
NK005(ca)011:1278: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)011:1281: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas yab yum phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK005(ca)011:1282: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis drangs 'khyud sbyar
NK005(ca)011:1283: nas mnyes par byas te h+aum yig glur len cing
NK005(ca)011:1284: bsrubs la / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa
NK005(ca)011:1285: a nu r+aa ga na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa
NK005(ca)011:1287: zhes snyoms par zhugs lus gnas kyi byang sems am
NK005(ca)011:1288: gis bsdus shing h+aum gis bskul nas dga' bzhi'i gnas
NK005(ca)011:1289: su nges shes kyis zin pa las lhan skyes kyi
NK005(ca)011:1290: bde ba brtan par byas te /
NK005(ca)011:1291: phata ces yum gyi mkha' la phab pa'i byang sems
NK005(ca)011:1292: snod du bzung ba bdud rtsir sbyar nas gcig la
NK005(ca)011:1293: gcig stob cing longs spyod du bcug la /
NK005(ca)011:1294: rig pa 'di dang rtag par mi 'bral bar gyis shig /
NK005(ca)011:1296: de ltar gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du byang sems bde ba chen pos dbang bskul bas /
NK005(ca)011:1297: sems kyi dri ma dag nas sangs rgyas kun dang
NK005(ca)011:1298: skal ba mnyam zhing bde ba chen po'i ye shes
NK005(ca)011:1299: la longs spyod pa'i mthu dang ldan par byas pa'o
NK005(ca)011:1300: // de nas slob mas me tog phul te mchod nas /
NK005(ca)011:1301: ston mchog rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK005(ca)011:1302: bdag gzhan kun la phan pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)011:1303: bla med dam tshig mchog nyid kyis //
NK005(ca)011:1304: bka' yi lung rnams gnang bar mdzod //
NK005(ca)011:1306: slob dpon gyis slob ma'i lce la byang sems bzhag nas dam tshig dpog pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:1307: khyod kyis srog chags bsad par bya //
NK005(ca)011:1308: rdzun gyi tshig kyang smra bar bya //
NK005(ca)011:1309: ma byin pa yang khyod kyis blang //
NK005(ca)011:1310: bud med dag kyang brten par bya //
NK005(ca)011:1311: rdo rje'i lam ni 'di dag gis //
NK005(ca)011:1312: sems can thams cad bskul bar bya //
NK005(ca)011:1313: dka' thub kyis ni gzir mi bya //
NK005(ca)011:1314: ci bde bar ni bde bar spyad //
NK005(ca)011:1315: 'di ni sangs rgyas byed spyod yin //
NK005(ca)011:1316: rnal 'byor longs spyod thams cad la //
NK005(ca)011:1317: cis kyang mi 'jigs dga' bar gyis //
NK005(ca)011:1318: sdig pa med kyis khyod la 'jigs //
NK005(ca)011:1320: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:1321: skye bo gang dag dam la 'god //
NK005(ca)011:1322: brtul zhugs khyod kyis de drongs la //
NK005(ca)011:1323: khrag chen po ni 'thung bar gyi //
NK005(ca)011:1324: skal ngan 'jig rten nyan thos la //
NK005(ca)011:1325: nam yang dga' bar mi bya ste //
NK005(ca)011:1326: skal bzang rdo rje sems dpa' gtso //
NK005(ca)011:1327: khyod kyis rtag tu bsgrub par gyis //
NK005(ca)011:1328: zhes rgyud las 'byung ba bzhin brjod par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:1329: bzhi pa gsang chen rdzogs pa'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)011:1330: sgom lung bka'i man ngag dang /
NK005(ca)011:1331: snying po sgrub pa'i man ngag sbyin pa gnyis kyis ston pa ste /
NK005(ca)011:1332: mtha' chod pa ni gzhan las shes par bya zhing /
NK005(ca)011:1333: snying por dril na shes bya'i chos thams cad sems su thag bcad /
NK005(ca)011:1334: de yang ngo bor stong nyid nam mkha' ltar gsal la mi rtog pa chos sku /
NK005(ca)011:1335: rang bzhin 'gag med chen po lha skur 'char ba longs sku /
NK005(ca)011:1336: thugs rje'i bye brag sangs rgyas kyi phrin las rgyun mi chad par 'byung ba sprul pa'i sku ste /
NK005(ca)011:1337: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK005(ca)011:1338: sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus pa //
NK005(ca)011:1339: rnal 'byor zab mo sku gsum rdzogs //
NK005(ca)011:1340: zhes gsungs pas 'di kho na phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK005(ca)011:1341: rigs kyi bu 'di ltar shes par gyis shig /
NK005(ca)011:1343: brjod bral 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK005(ca)011:1345: bdag dang gzhan don mi phyed pas //
NK005(ca)011:1346: sgyu ma lhun grub yum la rol //
NK005(ca)011:1347: zhes pa ltar lta bas thag bcad nas /
NK005(ca)011:1348: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba la bslab par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:1349: de ltar gsang chen de kho na nyid chos kyi
NK005(ca)011:1350: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ba
NK005(ca)011:1351: / rtog pa'i dri ma zag pa dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)011:1352: sangs shing zag pa med pa'i ye shes kyi sku
NK005(ca)011:1353: sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul du rgyas pas dpe chu zla
NK005(ca)011:1354: ltar snang stong dbyer med chos kyi dbyings su rnam
NK005(ca)011:1355: par dag cing rig pa gdeng du gyur pa'i mthu
NK005(ca)011:1357: de nas rjes dam tshig bsgrag pa ni /
NK005(ca)011:1359: dbang thob mdzes pa de dag gis //
NK005(ca)011:1360: dul ba'i sems su bzhag nas ni //
NK005(ca)011:1361: dam tshig chen po nye bar gnas //
NK005(ca)011:1363: dper na skyes bu bzang po rin po che'i brgyan na shin tu yang mdzes pa bzhin du /
NK005(ca)011:1364: snod dang ldan pa'i slob ma la bcud ldan gyi
NK005(ca)011:1365: slob dpon gyis phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang bskur te
NK005(ca)011:1367: dbang thob pa des kyang 'phral du khengs sems kyi nga rgyal mi bskyed /
NK005(ca)011:1368: yun du nyon mongs pa'i dbang du ma song bar bya zhing /
NK005(ca)011:1369: spyod lam shin tu bag yod dang khrel 'dzem chen
NK005(ca)011:1370: pos spyi dang khyad par dang lhag pa'i dam tshig
NK005(ca)011:1371: rnams tshul bzhin bsrung ba la nan tan du gyis
NK005(ca)011:1374: gtso bos ji ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK005(ca)011:1376: gtang rag gi man+dala phul nas /
NK005(ca)011:1377: mos pa dang dad pa dang mgu ba'i sems kyis
NK005(ca)011:1378: yon gyi dngos po ji ltar 'byor pa dag ci
NK005(ca)011:1379: nus su phul ba dge ba bsngo ba rnams bya'o
NK005(ca)011:1380: // tshogs mchod la sogs pa rjes kyi cho ga rnams ni dkyil chog las shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)011:1381: rnal 'byor ma rgyud rgya mtsho'i bla ma mchog /
NK005(ca)011:1382: rigs drug dkyil 'khor che las he ru ka'i //
NK005(ca)011:1383: snying po'i grong khyer mchog tu bder 'khrid pa'i //
NK005(ca)011:1384: cho ga bklags chog 'jug bde'i khrigs su bkod //
NK005(ca)011:1385: zab yang gzhung don nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor 'dra //
NK005(ca)011:1386: thos chung blo mthu khab kyi mig lta bus //
NK005(ca)011:1387: gzhal bar rlom pa ngal ba'i gnas nyid de //
NK005(ca)011:1388: 'on kyang lhag pa'i bsam pa kho nas so //
NK005(ca)011:1389: 'di las bsod nams dngos po gang thob des //
NK005(ca)011:1390: chos tshul mchog 'di dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK005(ca)011:1391: de las 'gro kun dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK005(ca)011:1392: go 'phang bde chen rdo rje'i gnas thob shog /
NK005(ca)011:1393: dpal chen yang dag lha dgu'i dbang gi cho ga bde chen 'jug ngogs zhes bya ba 'di ni /
NK005(ca)011:1394: kun bzang chos gling 'dus sde'i slob dpon pa sdom brtson bstan 'dzin 'gyur med dang /
NK005(ca)011:1395: mdo khams pa o rgyan mkhyen rab kyis bskul ba dang /
NK005(ca)011:1396: sngon chad 'jug bde'i dbang chog khrigs bkod mi 'dug pas /
NK005(ca)011:1397: chos tshul 'di nyid 'phel rgyas kyi sgor 'gyur bar dmigs te /
NK005(ca)011:1398: rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo rjes slob dpon
NK005(ca)011:1399: chen po h'u mdzad dang pad+ma sam b+ha wa'i gzhung
NK005(ca)011:1400: 'grel cha lag dang bcas pa rnams la legs par
NK005(ca)011:1402: phyogs tsam mthong ba dag o rgyan smin grol gling
NK005(ca)011:1403: gi bla brang chos 'khor lhun por rnam gnon gyi
NK005(ca)011:1404: lo gro bzhin gyi zla ba'i yar tshes dge ba
NK005(ca)011:1406: de ltar gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i gsung sor bzhag las /
NK005(ca)011:1407: gzhan du zhal 'phen mdzad pa rnams dkyus su bkod nas bklags chog mar bgyis pa 'di yang /
NK005(ca)011:1408: chos smra ba'i btsun pa gzhan phan mtha' yas pas
NK005(ca)011:1409: snga 'gyur bka' ma'i skor rnams phyogs gcig tu bsdu
NK005(ca)011:1410: ba'i skabs su 'di nyid kyi gzhung phyi mo slob
NK005(ca)011:1411: dpon h'u mdzad kyi dbang chog dang he ru ka
NK005(ca)011:1412: galpo mchan 'grel dang bcas pa la'ang legs par bstun
NK005(ca)011:1413: nas zhus shing dag par byas te gtan la phab
